 189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"score\": 0.9999999999813554, \"rank\": 1.7299581636485045e-11, \"text\": \"Iga\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Australian Open\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 160}, {\"ngram\": \"Roland Garros\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 240}, {\"ngram\": \"the semi\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 252}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 253, \"to\": 259}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, although the final was tighter than the scoreline suggested, Zheng ensured she took top spot on the podium by seeing off Croatian Vekic 6-2 6-3, with Swiatek having to settle for bronze.\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 357, \"end\": 362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.438827586021732e-22, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}, {\"begin\": 417, \"end\": 425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999866339050787, \"rank\": 6.9665427666290546e-06, \"text\": \"Croatian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scoreline\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 345}, {\"ngram\": \"top spot\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 402}, {\"ngram\": \"Swiatek\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold in the men's doubles went to Australian veterans Matt Ebden and John Peers, who defeated American duo Austin Krajicek and Rajeev Ram 6-7 (6-8) 7-6 (7-1) (10-8) in an extremely tight final.\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 677, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 518, \"end\": 528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.5551552028185509, \"rank\": 0.7374138481547625, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 538, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Ebden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Ebden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Ebden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Ebden\"}, {\"begin\": 553, \"end\": 563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Peers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Peers\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Peers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Peers\"}, {\"begin\": 578, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998252084339105, \"rank\": 8.055554024179487e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Austin Krajicek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\"}, {\"begin\": 611, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rajeev Ram\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gold\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 488}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's doubles\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ebden's Olympics began with a 6-0 6-1 drubbing in singles by Novak Djokovic after he took up an alternate position despite not having played a match in the format for two years.\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 740, \"end\": 754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ebden's Olympics\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 695}, {\"ngram\": \"a 6-0 6-1 drubbing\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 725}, {\"ngram\": \"singles\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"an alternate position\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 793}, {\"ngram\": \"a match\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"the format\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Last night, I was actually dreaming of an Instagram post: how it started, and how it's going,\\\" said the 36-year-old.\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 901, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.869953430990497e-14, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was thinking of my score eight days ago, winning one game.\", \"from\": 977, \"t